405-00-001	Middleware Workload Placement	
Where applicable, the current Middleware Workload Placemat should be referenced to identify utilization of appropriate enterprise tooling based on organizational alignment.

Steps:

Find your business unit / functional area in column 1.
Determine use case (BPM, Service, API, or Messaging)
Not sure or have questions? Ask an Architect
Follow business unit and use case to a solution.
Follow the technical tooling track to build your Middleware component.
Note: Workload Placemat represents existing state – i.e., the placemat should recommend where teams are already building, and there should not be any change to existing development process.

If placemat is giving a different result than expected, kindly request a consultation from the Middleware Governance team.

